icRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "In the Name of Allah, the most Gracious, the most Merciful.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "(Shuru karta hu) Allah ke naam se Jo bada maher-baan nehaayat rahem karne waala hai.", "Urdu": "اللہ کے نام سے (شروع کرتا ہوں) جو بڑا مہربا ن نہایت رحم کرنے والا ہے۔", "RArabic": "BISMILLAAHIR RAHMAANIR RAHEEM", "ArabicText1": "بِسْمِ اللہِ الرَّحْمٰنِ الرَّحِیْمِ", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012608, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": "INSHA-ALLAH COMING SOON", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Mere Allah! Kitne hi dushmano ne mere liye chhuri ki dhaar tez ki, aur mere liye har talwaar bhi khainchi, aur mere liye zaher'e qaatil ghol kar tayyaar ki, lekin meri nigheh-baani karne waali aankh nahi sooee, pas Tu ne jab meri kamzori dekhi keh mai un na-gawaariyo’n ko sahe (bardaasht kar) nahi sakta, un tabah-kun saathiyo’n ke saamne aajiz (majboor) hu, Tu ne un sab ko apni taaqat se bar-taraf kar diya mujh mein itni quwwat o taaqat nahi thi, phir Tu ne usey us gadhe (khadde) mein phenka jo us ne mere liye khoda wa apni baat mein na-kaam raha.", "Urdu": "میرے اﷲکتنے ہی دشمنوں نے میرے لئے چھری کی دھار تیز کی اور میرے لئے ہر تلوار کھینچی اور میرے لئے زہر ِقاتل گھول کر تیار کیا لیکن میری نگہبانی کرنے والی آنکھ نہیں سوئی پس تو نے جب میری کمزوری دیکھی کہ میں ان ناگواریوں کو سہہ نہیں سکتا ان تباہ کن سختیوں کے سامنے عاجز ہوں تو نے ان سب کو اپنی قوت وطاقت سے برطرف کر دیا مجھ میں اتنی قوت وطاقت نہیں تھی پھر تو نے اسے اس گڑھے میں پھینکاجو اس نے میرے لئے کھودا وہ اپنی بات میں ناکام رہا۔", "RArabic": "ILAAHEE KAM MIN A’DOO-WIN SHA-HAZA LEE ZOBA-TA MUDYATE-HI WA AR-HAFA LEE SHABAA HADDE-HI WA DAAFE LEE QAWAA-TELA SOMOO-MEHI WA LAM TA-NAM A’NNEE A’IY-NO HARAA-SATEHI FA-LAMMAA RA-AIY-TA ZA’FEE A’NEH TEMAA-LIL FA-WAADE-HE WA A’JZEE A’N MOLIM-MAATIL JAWAAA'e HE SARAF-TA ZAA-LEKA A’NNAA BE-HAWALE-KA LAA BE-HAWLEEN MINNEE WA LAA QUWWATIN FA-ALQAIY-TAHU FIL HAFEE-RIL LAZIH TAFARA-HU LEE KHAAA'e BAN MIMMAA AMMA-LAHU.", "ArabicText1": "اِلٰهِىْ كَمْ مِنْ عَدُوٍّ شَحَذَ لِىْ ظُبَةَ مُدْيَتِهٖ وَاَرْهَفَ لِىْ شَبَا حَدِّهٖ وَدَافَ لِىْ قَوَاتِلَ سُمُوْمِهٖ وَلَمْ تَنَمْ عَنِّىْ عَيْنُ حِرَاسَتِةٖ فَلَمَّا رَاَيْتَ ضَعْفِىْ عَنِ احْتِمَالِ الْفَوَادِحِ وَعَجْزِىْ عَنْ مُلِمَّاتِ الْجَوَاۗئِحِ صَرَفْتَ ذٰلِكَ عَنّٰى بِحَوَلِكَ وَقُوَّتِكَ لَا بِحَوْلٍ مِنِّىْ وَلَا قُوَّةٍ فَاَلْقَيْتَهٗ فِى الْحَفِيْرِ الَّذِى احْتَفَرَهٗ لِىْ خَاۗئِبًا مِمَّا اَمَّلَهٗ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "ArabicText13": null, "ArabicGreenSign13": null, "ArabicRedSign13": null, "ArabicBlueSign13": null, "ArabicText14": null, "ArabicGreenSign14": null, "ArabicRedSign14": null, "ArabicBlueSign14": null, "ArabicText15": null, "ArabicGreenSign15": null, "ArabicRedSign15": null, "ArabicBlueSign15": null, "ArabicText16": null, "ArabicGreenSign16": null, "ArabicRedSign16": null, "ArabicBlueSign16": null, "ArabicText17": null, "ArabicGreenSign17": null, "ArabicRedSign17": null, "ArabicBlueSign17": null, "ArabicText18": null, "ArabicGreenSign18": null, "ArabicRedSign18": null, "ArabicBlueSign18": null, "ArabicText19": null, "ArabicGreenSign19": null, "ArabicRedSign19": null, "ArabicBlueSign19": null, "ArabicText20": null, "ArabicGreenSign20": null, "ArabicRedSign20": null, "ArabicBlueSign20": null, "EnglishImage": null, "GujaratiImage": null, "RUrduImage": null, "UrduImage": null, "IsRed": 0, "MinimizeDescriptionLine": 0, "IsPrintable": 0}, {"Id": 1012609, "EnglishTitle": null, "GujaratiTitle": null, "RUrduTitle": null, "UrduTitle": null, "Sequence": null, "EnglishDescription": null, "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": null, "UrduDescription": null, "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": "Is duniya jaha mein aur aakherat mein bhi na-muraad hi raha. Pas Tere liye hamd hai us maher-baani par, ay mere Aaqa jitni hamd Teri shaan ke laaeq hai. Ay Ma’bood! Apne ghalbe ke saath usey pakad aur apni qudrat se uski talwaar ko mujh se hata de, Tu usey kisi taraf laga de keh usi mein laga rahe aur us cheez mein aajeez kar de jo woh chahta hai.", "Urdu": "اس دنیا میں اور آخرت میں بھی نامراد ہی رہا پس تیرےلیے حمد ہے اس مہربانی پر اے میرے آقا جتنی حمد تیری شان کےلائق ہے اے معبود! اپنے غلبے کے ساتھ اسے پکڑے اور اپنی قدرت سے اس کی تلوار کو مجھ سے ہٹادے تو اسے کسی طرف لگا دے کہ اسی میں لگا رہے اور اس چیز میں عاجز کر دے جو وہ چاہتا ہے۔", "RArabic": "FID DUNYAA MOTABAA-E-DAN MIMMAA RAJAA-HO FIL AAKHERATE FALA-KAL HAMDO A’LAA ZAALE-KA QADRA ISTEH-QAAQE-KA SAYYEDEE. ALLAAHUMMA FA-KHUZ-HO BE-IZZATE-KA WAF-LUL HADDA-HU A’NNEE BE-QUDRATE-KA WAJ-A’L LAHU SHUGH-LAN FEE-MAA YALEE-HE WA A’J-ZAN A’MMAA YONAA-WEEHE.", "ArabicText1": "فِى الدُّنْيَا مُتَبَاعِدًا مِمَّا رَجَاهُ فِى الْآخِرَةِ فَلَكَ الْحَمْدُ عَلٰى ذٰلِكَ قَدْرَ اِسْتِحْقَاقِكَ سَيِّدِىْ۔ اَللّٰهُمَّ فَخُذْهُ بِعِزَّتِكَ وَافْلُلْ حَدَّهٗ عَنِّىْ بِقُدْرَتِكَ وَاجْعَلْ لَهٗ شُغْلًا فِيْمَا يَلِيْهِ وَعَجْزًا عَمَّا يُنَاوِيْهِ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4":